nodes.text: Cam Kennedy was the illustrator of the Star Wars: Dark Empire, Star Wars: Dark Empire II and most of the Star Wars: Boba Fett comics series. He also illustrated Empire 7 and the covers for Classic Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back 2, Jabba the Hutt: The Gaar Suppoon Hit and Star Wars Tales 18. Kennedy was born and raised in Scotland and spent seven years painting in France before becoming a comic artist.
